oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Dickey Lee Live at the Lone Star Café - 1978-07-17
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is from the Lone Star Café live show. The tape features a live performance of Dickey Lee (musician). The Lone Star Café show is presented by Mort Cooperman, Bill McGivney and the WHN radio network. The recording of Dickey Lee is from July 17, 1978.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Dickey Lee
